      "platform": "TV",
      "onair_date": "1980-10-02",
      "alias": [
        "Galaxy Express: Can You Love Like a Mother?",
        "Ginga Tetsudou 999: Kimi wa Haha no You ni Aiseruka!!",
        "銀河鉄道999 君は母のように愛せるか!!",
        "银河铁道999：你能像母亲一样爱着吗"
